  m_TableData:
  - m_Id: 1
    m_Localized: The new Bitecraft update sucks. Period
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2
    m_Localized: 'New Fishmon games are so simple, they make it way to easy for the
      pups '
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 3
    m_Localized: DONT TALK TO ME!!! I am locking in for Overswim for next 5 hours!!!!
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 4
    m_Localized: Why do I always have pups in my Bite of Duty lobbies????
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 5
    m_Localized: Sharknite collab with One Teeth goes crazy hard!
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 6
    m_Localized: Objectively correct Fishmon game tier list
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 7
    m_Localized: bro really thought he could 1v1 me in Sharknite and not get absolutely
      chomped #neveragain
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 8
    m_Localized: Overswims new hero is way too overpowered?! What were the devs thinking?!
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 9
    m_Localized: I wanna go on a Bitecraft date so badly
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 10
    m_Localized: 'FINFA career mode is the only mode that matters and I will not
      be taking questions

'
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 11
    m_Localized: 'Dont talk to me if you havent played THE GAME that Cult of the
      Swarm is '
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 12
    m_Localized: "Deep Sea Exploration 33\xB4s soundtrack is actually a masterpiece"
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 13
    m_Localized: Still cant believe they turned Sonic the Blueshark into a movie,
      how will they adapt the masterpiece the game is?
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 14
    m_Localized: MrFeast really said let me spend a million dollars just to give
      it away, respect the reef honestly
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 15
    m_Localized: Among Fins really broke friendships worldwide and we all just accepted
      it and moved on
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 16
    m_Localized: "MrFeast\xB4s is really trying stay relevant after that failed waterpark
      of his! "
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 17
    m_Localized: My Jawblox gf just broke up with me! How can I get her back without
      looking like a shrimp?
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 18
    m_Localized: I really ate in Dress to Digest #JawBlox #GiveMeJawbuxxxx
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 19
    m_Localized: Bro why did no one tell me that jawbux cost actual money????
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  references:
